
<%- layout("/layouts/boierplate") %>  
<body>

    <!-- Carousel -->
    <div id="carouselExample" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
        <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img src="https://wallpapercave.com/wp/wp2024281.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Image 1">
                <div class="carousel-caption">
                    <h1>Indian farming feeds the nation and powers its economy.</h1>
                    <p>From rice paddies to cotton fields, farmers shape our future.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="https://indiaforensic.com/certifications/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/agriculture.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Image 2">
                <div class="carousel-caption">
                    <h1>Tech-driven farming is transforming India's agriculture.</h1>
                    <p>Precision tools and sustainable methods boost productivity.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="https://ijlmh.com/wp-content/uploads/19.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Image 3">
                <div class="carousel-caption">
                    <h1>Tradition meets innovation in India's diverse farmlands.</h1>
                    <p>Farmers preserve culture while embracing modern solutions.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExample" data-bs-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
        </button>
        <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExample" data-bs-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
        </button>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Statistics Section -->
    <div class="container my-5 text-center">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card p-3">
                    <h2>Registered Farmers</h2>
                    <p id="farmers-count">Loading...</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card p-3">
                    <h2>Registered Crops</h2>
                    <p id="crops-count">Loading...</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card p-3">
                    <h2>Registered Users</h2>
                    <p id="users-count">Loading...</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Card Section -->
    <div class="container my-5">
        <div class="row g-4">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card">
                    <img src="image/crop1.jpeg" class="card-img-top" alt="Vegetables">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h3 class="card-title">Vegetables</h3>
                        <p class="card-text">Vegetables are edible plant parts including roots, stems, leaves, and sometimes flowers. They are rich in essential nutrients like vitamins, minerals, and fiber, making them crucial for a balanced diet.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card">
                    <img src="image/crop2.jpeg" class="card-img-top" alt="Fruits">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h3 class="card-title">Fruits</h3>
                        <p class="card-text">Fruits are the mature ovary of flowering plants, typically sweet or sour. They are consumed for their refreshing taste and nutritional value, rich in vitamins and antioxidants.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card">
                    <img src="image/crop3.jpeg" class="card-img-top" alt="Grains">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h3 class="card-title">Grains</h3>
                        <p class="card-text">Grains are small, hard seeds harvested primarily for food, providing a major source of carbohydrates. They are staple diets in many cultures, with rice, wheat, and oats widely consumed.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card">
                    <img src="image/crop4.jpeg" class="card-img-top" alt="Beans">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h3 class="card-title">Beans</h3>
                        <p class="card-text">Beans, belonging to the legume family, are a rich source of protein and fiber. They are versatile and used in soups, stews, and various dishes worldwide.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Features Section -->
    <div class="container my-5">
        <div class="row g-4">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card text-center">
                    <img src="https://zeracreative.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/8-Ways-to-Make-Your-Website-More-User-Friendly.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="User-Friendly Interface">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h3 class="card-title">User-Friendly Interface</h3>
                        <p class="card-text">Our app boasts an intuitive design that enhances user experience, making navigation a breeze for everyone, regardless of tech-savviness.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card text-center">
                    <img src="https://ik.imagekit.io/botpenguin/assets/website/Real_Time_Communication_e0da5ad85f.webp" class="card-img-top" alt="Real-Time Communication">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h3 class="card-title">Real-Time Communication</h3>
                        <p class="card-text">Stay updated with instant alerts. Get notified about important events, changes, and reminders in real-time, ensuring you never miss a beat.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card text-center">
                    <img src="https://www.soscanhelp.com/hubfs/Network%20Security%20Header.png" class="card-img-top" alt="Enhanced Security Features">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h3 class="card-title">Enhanced Security Features</h3>
                        <p class="card-text">Protect your data with advanced encryption protocols and multi-factor authentication, offering peace of mind and safeguarding your personal information.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card text-center">
                    <img src="https://webapphuddle.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/to-do-dashboard.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="Customizable Dashboard">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h3 class="card-title">Customizable Dashboard</h3>
                        <p class="card-text">Tailor your dashboard to display the information that matters most to you. Organize widgets, charts, and key metrics for a personalized experience.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Maps Section -->
    <div class="container text-center my-5">
        <img src="https://www.netmaps.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/india-Agricultural-map.png" class="img-fluid my-3" alt="Agriculture Map">
        <img src="https://cdn3.vectorstock.com/i/1000x1000/50/72/agricultural-smart-farm-flowchart-with-images-vector-27385072.jpg" class="img-fluid my-3" alt="Agriculture Flow">
    </div>
    
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    </body>